hopobject.body: Languages anavar before and after pics female And the sedentary lifestyle has now taken over. At the age of 13, few are very active. Some 85% of girls and 73% of boys say they do not do even an hour's physical activity a day, which is the recommended minimum. Nearly three-quarters of 13-year-olds (68% of girls and 74% of boys) say they watch at least two hours of TV on a week day, leaving less time for sport and physical activity. Around a quarter of children (23% of boys and 25% of girls) spend at least six hours sitting down on Saturday and Sunday.
